metadata.name: Maquis
metadata.description:
Maquis
In an abandoned factory in the distance, I saw poppies.
I thought a lot about my states, trying to decipher what the Worlds were telling me.  
I went over and picked up a sheet of cardboard in the children's drawing studio...
And with my finger, in acrylic paint, I expressed what I was feeling. 
And the poppies just stood there in the distance...
